        "text": "Black Flame Blade is a Incantation spell in Elden Ring. Read on to learn more about Black Flame Blade's effects, stat requirements, how to get Black Flame Blade, and tips and tricks on how to use it effectively!\n\nBlack Flame Blade Overview\n\nStats and Requirements\n\nBlack Flame Blade Effect Enchants right-hand armament with black flame. Spell Type FP Cost Slots Used Incantation 15 1 Stat Requirements Intelligence Faith Arcane 0 17 0\n\nBlack Flame Blade Lore\n\nLore Description \"A black flame incantation of the Godskin Apostles.\n\nEngulfs armament held in the right hand with black flame. This incantation can be cast without delay after performing another action.\n\nBlack flame is weighty. After dealing damage it continues to sap foes' HP for a very short time.\"\n\nBlack Flame Blade Effects\n\nBlack Flame Blade is a Godskin Apostle Incantation that grants the user the ability to temporarily imbue their right-hand weapon in black flame for 7 seconds that increases its damage. While active, enemies will take fire damage initially and over time.\n\nHow to Get Black Flame Blade\n\nPurchased from Corhyn\n\nView Full Image View Full Image\n\nBlack Flame Blade can be bought from Corhyn for 7500 runes after giving him the Godskin Prayerbook that can be found in Stormveil Castle.\n\nTo get the Godskin Prayerbook, travel to the Liftside Chamber site of grace and head outside to where the enemies are. If you stick to the right, you'll eventually come across a flight of stairs leading down. At the end will be a fog gate with rats guarding it, and you will need a stonesword key to unlock it and obtain the prayerbook in one of the chests inside.\n\nHow to Use Black Flame Blade\n\nBuff Damage of your Attacks\n\nThis spell is best used before initiating a fight to buff and increase the damage you can deal to your enemies. it is effective against bosses and enemies with large health pools since the burning effect of the black flame deals 2% or more damage to their max HP.\n\nIt can also be used during fights for continued increased fire damage since the spell has a relatively fast casting time. Make sure to perform this after successfully dodging or baiting out an enemy's attack since you can still be hit during cast.\n\nPair with Godslayer Seal\n\nGodskin Apostle Incantations are best paired with the Godslayer Seal as it will boost the effectiveness of these Incantations.\n\nElden Ring Related Guides\n\nList of All Magic Spells\n\nIncantations\n\nAll Legendary Incantations\n\nBeast Claw Cure Poison Dragonfire Greyoll's Roar Heal Litany of Proper Death Catch Flame Rejection The Flame of Frenzy Urgent Heal Dragonclaw Dragonice Glintstone Breath Rotten Breath Dragonmaw Frozen Lightning Spear Fortissax's Lightning Spear Lansseax's Glaive Howl of Shabriri Bestial Sling Poison Mist Order's Blade Magic Fortification Flame Fortification Flame Sling O, Flame! Surge, O Flame! Flame, Cleanse Me Smarag's Glintstone Breath Ekzykes's Decay Aspects of the Crucible: Tail Aspects of the Crucible: Horns Flame of the Fell God Whirl, O Flame! Order Healing Darkness Scouring Black Flame Assassin's Approach Protection of the Erdtree Golden Vow Lightning Fortification Great Heal Discus of Light Noble Presence Lord's Heal Lord's Aid Divine Fortification Lightning Strike Bloodflame Blade Poison Armament Black Flame Black Flame Blade Lightning Spear Black Blade Flame, Fall Upon Them Flame, Grant Me Strength Flame, Protect Me Giantsflame Take Thee Burn, O Flame! Black Flame Ritual Black Flame's Protection Bloodboon Barrier of Gold Wrath of Gold Erdtree Heal Blessing's Boon Blessing of the Erdtree Lord's Divine Fortification Triple Rings of Light Radagon's Rings of Light Elden Stars Law of Regression Immutable Shield Law of Causality Stone of Gurranq Gurranq's Beast Claw Bestial Vitality Bestial Constitution Ancient Dragons' Lightning Strike Honed Bolt Ancient Dragons' Lightning Spear Electrify Armament Vyke's Dragonbolt Dragonbolt Blessing Agheel